data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom / 2.5 bath, plus loft, in the highly desirable Gilbert Power Ranch community. The great room showcases new laminate floors, with a comfortable and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is equipped with white cabinetry, a subway tile backsplash, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a practical center island, that doubles as a breakfast bar. The master bedroom is a private retreat, offering direct access to the balcony and an ensuite bathroom, complete with dual sinks and a relaxing tub. A versatile loft space, fitted with built-in cabinets, serves perfectly as an office or entertainment area. The backyard oasis is designed for enjoyment with a covered patio, a cozy seating area, and a refreshing pool with waterfall feature. Priced aggressively to sell quickly!!!
